extend includes/layout.pug
block append customizations
    - activePage='Home'
block content
    main(
        class=`
            mx-auto
            max-w-[100rem]
            flex flex-col xl:flex-row
            items-center xl:justify-between
            mt-6 md:mt-20 xl:mt-80
            px-6 md:px-44
            space-y-20 md:space-y-36 xl:space-y-0
        `)
        article.text-white.max-w-md(
            class=`
                text-center xl:text-left
            `)
            p.uppercase.text-indigo-200.font-barlow-condensed.tracking-widest(
                class=`
                    md:text-xl xl:text-3xl
                `).
                So, you want to travel to
            p.uppercase.text-white.font-bellefair(
                class=`
                    text-[5.5rem] md:text-10xl
                    tracking-[2.7px] md:tracking-normal`
                    ).
                Space
            p.text-description(
                class=`text-center xl:text-justify`).
                Let’s face it; if you want to go to space, you might as well genuinely go to
                outer space and not hover kind of on the edge of it. Well sit back, and relax
                because we’ll give you a truly out of this world experience!

        aside.flex.items-center.justify-center.rounded-full.bg-white(
            class=`
                w-36 h-36 md:w-60 md:h-60
            `)
            p.font-bellefair.uppercase.tracking-widest(
                class=`
                    text-xl md:text-3xl
                `) Explore
